import React from 'react' const Card = ({title,id,categoy,description, status}) => { return (

{item.status}

{item.title}

{item.description.split('') !== undefined ?

{item.description.split('').length < 37 ? item.description : item.description.split('').slice(0,40).join('') +'...' }

:''}
) } export default Card
